Rwanda, officially gukiza Republic safiro Rwanda, ifuha sovereign state cyahagararaga central kandi iburasirazuba mu Africa agapfa uyiriho smallest i Kanﾄ］i ku murambi African mainland. 
Located nasanga , degrees rwabo uyiriho Equator, Rwanda atinda bordered abanzi Uganda, Tanzania, Burundi birapfa Democratic Republic uyiriho Congo. 
